OL,3,CMan appears in court after three house
OL,4,Cfires in Leicestershire town
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court after
OL,7,Fthree house fires in a town in
OL,8,FLeicestershire.
OL,10,FThe three fires happened within
OL,11,Fminutes of each other in Ashby-De-La-
OL,12,FZouch, just after 7am - the first in
OL,13,FHolywell Avenue, the second in Prestop
OL,14,FDrive, and then in Clifton Drive.
OL,15,FPolice believe they are linked.
OL,17,FTwo teenagers and a woman from one
OL,18,Fhouse in Holywell Avenue were taken to
OL,19,Fhospital on Friday morning (November
OL,20,F21st).
