OL,3,CMan appears in court after three house
OL,4,Cfires in Leicestershire town
OL,6,F50-year-old Karl Poxon, of Holywell
OL,7,FAvenue, was arrested and charged with
OL,8,Fthree counts of arson with intent to
OL,9,Fendanger life and dangerous driving.
OL,11,FHe was remanded in custody and will
OL,12,Fappear at Leicester Crown Court on
OL,13,FJanuary 12th, 2026.
